			<title>New Radius Distance Search Plugin and Search Module for Sobi2</title>
			<link>http://www.sigsiu.net/latest_news/new_radius_distance_search_plugin_and_search_module_for_sobi2.html</link>
			<description>We just released version 1.3.4 of the Radius Distance Search plugin which solves a problem with the search module.
Additionally version 2.2 of the Search Module for Joomla! 1.5 is available. This version fixes a problem with WebKit based browsers (Safari and Chrome).

The Radius Distance Search Plugin is a plugin for Sobi2, that allows adding proximity search easily to the existing search form in Sobi2 - Description of the Plugin (/addons/radius_distance_search_plugin.html).
The Search Module is an interface module to standard Sobi2 search which can be placed in every Joomla! module position.

See here for plugin update instructions (/faq/how_to_update_a_sobi2_plugin.html) and for the full changelog list of the Radius Plugin (https://shop.sigsiu.net/en/manuals/radius-distance-search-plugin/changelog) and full changelog list of the Search Module (https://shop.sigsiu.net/en/manuals/search-module/changelog) in the documentation section Manuals and more.... (https://shop.sigsiu.net/en/manuals).

If you bought the Radius Distance Search Plugin or the Search Module, you can download the new version within your upgrade period from our shop.
</description>
