		<item>
			<title>Version 1.3 of Radius Distance Search Plugin available</title>
			<link>http://www.sigsiu.net/latest_news/version_1.3_of_radius_distance_search_plugin_available.html</link>
			<description>We released version 1.3 of the Radius Distance Search Plugin today.
This version is a maintenance release which contains several minor bug fixes as XHTML compliance changes and it solves a problem using postal codes. Functions, deprecated in PHP 5.3 are removed as well as ISO coded language files. Several texts are changed to more common expressions.
Also it is now possible to define a fixed search distance instead of the user selects the distance from a distance select box.

The Radius Distance Search Plugin is a plugin for Sobi2, that allows adding proximity search easily to the existing search form in Sobi2 - Description of the Plugin (/addons/radius_distance_search_plugin.html).

See here for upgrading instructions (/upgrading.html) and for the full changelog list (https://shop.sigsiu.net/en/manuals/radius-distance-search-plugin/changelog.html) in the documentation section Manuals and more.... (https://shop.sigsiu.net/en/manuals/index.html).

If you bought the Radius Distance Search Plugin you can download the new version within your upgrade period from our shop.
</description>
